<p>

<b>Jonah Hill</b> (born <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../849/8849.xml">
December 20</link>, <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../755/34755.xml">
1983</link>) is an <body wordnetid="107965085" confidence="0.8">
<social_group wordnetid="107950920" confidence="0.8">
<political_orientation wordnetid="106212839" confidence="0.8">
<colony wordnetid="108374049" confidence="0.8">
