American</link></democracy>
</group>
</political_unit>
</state>
</colony>
</political_orientation>
</social_group>
</body>
 actor and <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../997/1137997.xml">
screenwriter</link>.  Hill has had a successful career as an actor in comedic films, appearing in roles in the films <it><link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../611/5444611.xml">
Accepted</link></it>, <it><movie wordnetid="106613686" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../176/3572176.xml">
Grandma's Boy</link></movie>
